      <title>日本采取行动允许投资基金持有加密货币</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/japan-moves-to-allow-investment-funds-to-hold-crypto</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在日本首相岸田文雄政府同意提交修订法案以实施这一变化后，日本距离允许风险投资公司和其他投资基金直接持有数字资产又近了一步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/japan-moves-to-allow-investment-funds-to-hold-crypto</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 11:35:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
