    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沙特阿美今年可能会出售债券，重点关注较长期的债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/aramco-may-sell-bonds-this-year-with-focus-on-long-maturities</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沙特阿美公司财务主管表示，随着金融市场有所改善，该公司今年可能会出售债券，并且该公司希望发行较长期的债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/aramco-may-sell-bonds-this-year-with-focus-on-long-maturities</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 09:50:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Forvia 将裁员 10,000 人，以更好地参与电动汽车转型</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/forvia-to-cut-10-000-jobs-to-better-compete-in-ev-transition</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Forvia SE 准备在未来五年内裁员约 13% 的欧洲员工，并计划利用人工智能在转向电动汽车的过程中更好地与亚洲竞争对手竞争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/forvia-to-cut-10-000-jobs-to-better-compete-in-ev-transition</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 09:29:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
